{{Quote|It took me the better part of eight years in Dorthus Tal prison on Sacorria to realize that, but I have realized it, and I'm a changed man as a result.|[[Thrackan Sal-Solo]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse" />}}
The '''Dorthus Tal Prison''' was a [[Prison/Legends|prison]] on the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core World]] of [[Sacorria]]. It was located on [[Dorthus Tal Island]], the same island as Sacorria's capital [[Dorthus Tal City]] and the warden was [[Kedar Blackgate]].<ref>[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]], pages 143-144</ref> It was powered by geothermal energy from a volcano. It had the reputation of being "escape proof." [[Thrackan Sal-Solo]] was imprisoned there from [[18 ABY/Legends|18]] to [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]].<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos II: Jedi Eclipse" />

